install concat npm package

concat or join data of multiple files into one 
"concat:css": "concat -o css/style.concat.css css/icon-font.css css/main.css"  -> css/style.concat.css created

using minify extension minify the file size by going to that file and pressing f1 and selecting minify. 
-> css/style.concat.min.css created

rename it styles.css and change the link in html files to styles.css then deploy.
